'''黃楊木蛾'''（{{lang-la|''Cydalima perspectalis''}}，{{lang-en|Box Tree Moth}}）在分類上屬於[[草螟科|草螟科]]的蛾種。牠在[[亞洲|亞洲]]﹙[[日本|日本]]、[[中國|中國]]、[[台灣|台灣]]、[[韓國|韓國]]、[[蘇俄|蘇俄]]遠東區及[[印度|印度]]﹚為本土種；<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.insekten-sachsen.de/Pages/TaxonomyBrowser.aspx?Id=442650 | title = Buchsbaumzünsler (Cydalima perspectalis (Walker, 1859)) | language = de | accessdate = 28 December 2013 | publisher = insekten-sachsen.de | archive-date = 2020-11-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201126232815/http://www.insekten-sachsen.de/Pages/TaxonomyBrowser.aspx?Id=442650 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 而在[[歐洲|歐洲]]為外來種。在歐洲，牠首先在2006年於[[德國|德國]]被發現，然後在2007年於[[瑞士|瑞士]]和[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]被發現，最後在2009年則於[[法國|法國]]、[[大不列顛|大不列顛]]和[[澳洲|澳洲]]被發現<ref>Landwirtschaftskammer Vorarlberg: [http://www.ogv.at/eXtraEngine3/WebObjects/eXtraEngine3.woa/wa/article?id=4180&rubricid=210&menuid=210&back=rp ''Buchsbaumzünsler wieder Aktiv.''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ogv.at/eXtraEngine3/WebObjects/eXtraEngine3.woa/wa/article?id=4180&rubricid=210&menuid=210&back=rp |date=20200401150525 }} In: ''Obst- und Gartenkultur Vorarlberg.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.faunaeur.org/full_results.php?id=442650 |title=Fauna Europaea |access-date=2014-01-05 |archive-date=2016-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823182323/http://www.faunaeur.org/full_results.php?id=442650 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Mally, R. & M. Nuss 2010: [http://www.eje.cz/scripts/viewabstract.php?abstract=1550 Phylogeny and nomenclature of the box tree moth, Cydalima perspectalis (Walker, 1859) comb. n., which was recently introduced into Europe (Lepidoptera: Pyraloidea: Crambidae: Spilomelinae)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eje.cz/scripts/viewabstract.php?abstract=1550 |date=20131230235119 }}. – European journal of Entomology 107 (3): 393–400.</ref>。在2011年時，黃楊木蛾於[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]<ref>Sáfián, Sz. & B. Horváth 2011: Box Tree Moth – Cydalima perspectalis (Walker, 1859), new member in the Lepidoptera fauna of Hungary (Lepidoptera: Crambidae). – Natura Somogyiensis 19: 245–246.</ref>、[[羅馬尼亞|羅馬尼亞]]<ref>Székely, L., V. Dinca & C. Mihai 2012: Cydalima perspectalis (Walker, 1859), a new species for the Romanian fauna (Lepidoptera: Crambidae: Spilomelinae). – Buletin de Informare Entomologica 22 (3–4): 73–77</ref>及[[土耳其|土耳其]] <ref>Hizal, E., M. Kose, C. Yesiland & D. Kaynar 2011: The New Pest Cydalima perspectalis (Walker, 1859) (Lepidoptera: Crambidae) in Turkey. – Journal of Animal and Veterinary Advances 11 (3): 400–403.</ref>第一次被發現。在[[斯洛伐克|斯洛伐克]]及[[比利時|比利時]]也陸續發現其蹤跡<ref>[http://webh01.ua.ac.be/vve/Checklists/Lepidoptera/Crambidae/Cperspectalis.htm Lepidoptera of Belgium] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230235256/http://webh01.ua.ac.be/vve/Checklists/Lepidoptera/Crambidae/Cperspectalis.htm |date=2013-12-30 }}</ref>；
在[[丹麥|丹麥]]最大島西蘭的數個地點，也於2013年發現其蹤跡。

黃楊木蛾的翼展寬度為40到45公厘，每年繁殖兩到三次，幼蟲的成長期為三、四月到九月。幼蟲的食物為[[黃楊科|黃楊科]]（Buxaceae）樹木的嫩葉或嫩支，在整個冬天的季節，幼蟲是以卵的形態保存著。

==對環境生態影響及蟲害防治==
